&lt;li&gt;Ownership-oriented. You keep workflows clean, follow up on open items without being asked, and treat the function like it&#39;s yours to run.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communicator. You surface what matters in a format others can act on, and you stay responsive to the teams that depend on you.&lt;/li&gt;
